      <title>JetSMART 增加飞机数量，助力 Milei 航空开通航线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/jetsmart-adds-to-argentina-fleet-as-milei-opens-up-the-skies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利总统哈维尔·米莱伊 (Javier Milei) 寻求放松航空业管制并打破这家旗舰航空公司在国内市场的主导地位，智利 JetSMART 航空有限公司 (JetSMART Airlines SpA) 正在增加其在阿根廷的飞机数量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/jetsmart-adds-to-argentina-fleet-as-milei-opens-up-the-skies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
