    <item>
      <title>债券交易员仔细研究美国就业数据，寻找美联储利率计划的线索</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/bond-traders-scour-us-jobs-data-for-clues-on-fed-s-rate-cut-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五受飓风和罢工影响的美国就业报告为下周美联储的政策决定提供了最后的线索，因此一直在对冲美国国债进一步下跌的投资者正在为波动做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/bond-traders-scour-us-jobs-data-for-clues-on-fed-s-rate-cut-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 01:20:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者关注美国大选，黄金价格在美国就业数据公布前上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/gold-xauusd-steadies-after-tumbling-from-record-as-rate-cut-bets-fade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员等待关键的美国就业数据，并在即将到来的总统大选前权衡潜在的市场混乱，金价从 7 月份以来的最大单日跌幅中反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/gold-xauusd-steadies-after-tumbling-from-record-as-rate-cut-bets-fade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 23:37:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市上涨，就业数据有望限制本周的波动：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五美国关键就业数据公布前，股市上涨。本周波动剧烈，科技巨头的收益喜忧参半，市场处于守势。中东局势再度紧张，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 22:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
