      <title>瑞士律师将不再承担举报黑钱的义务：部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/swiss-lawyers-won-t-face-duty-to-flag-dirty-money-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士财政部长表示，瑞士议会不太可能通过强制律师打击洗钱的规定，因为许多议员本身就是律师。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/swiss-lawyers-won-t-face-duty-to-flag-dirty-money-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 18:41:43 GMT</pubDate>
